---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Wunderelf Studios, an indie game studio where stories become adventures.">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About <span class="text-teal-light">Wunderelf</span> Studios</h1>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-teal mx-auto rounded-full" />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <p>
          Wunderelf Studios started the way a lot of good things do: someone wanted to build
          something they couldn't find anywhere else. By day, the work is computer architecture.
          By night and weekends, it's building worlds. The name? It came from a soccer sweatshirt
          where the bottom of the last "E" in "Wunderle" fell off, and "Wunderelf" was too good
          not to keep.
        </p>

        <p>
          The studio's debut title, <a href="/echoes-of-choice" class="text-teal-light hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium">Echoes of Choice</a>,
          grew from a simple console app into a full RPG. It pulls from a lifetime of favorite games
          and years of weekly D&amp;D sessions, combining the class systems, tactical combat, and
          branching storytelling that make those experiences unforgettable.
        </p>

        <p>
          We're committed to building games with care, one at a time, and creating worlds
          that players want to return to.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-dark-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gold mx-auto rounded-full" />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
            &#x1F3AF;
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text">Player Agency</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Choices should be real. When a player makes a decision, they should feel the weight of it.
              We build genuinely different paths, not the illusion of branching.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
            &#x2696;
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text">Depth Without Overwhelm</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Deep systems should feel inviting, not intimidating. We design complexity that
              reveals itself naturally, so players can start simple and grow into mastery.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
            &#x267F;
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text">Accessibility</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Great games should be playable by everyone. We build accessibility into
              our games from the start, not as an afterthought.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
